  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, then take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Cut your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into wedges</p><p>Add the<strong> potato wedges</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for 30 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1648027622315-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1648027622315-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1648027622315-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1648027622315-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1648027622315-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grate your <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Add a handful of <strong>flour </strong>to a plate and a splash of <strong>milk </strong>to a small bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>panko breadcrumbs </strong>to another plate with your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>dried oregano </strong>and<strong> half </strong>the <strong>grated cheese </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Add a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and mix together (this will make your breadcrumbs golden!)</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1648027625201-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1648027625201-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1648027625201-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1648027625201-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1648027625201-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Season your <strong>chicken breast strips </strong>with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> then coat in the <strong>flour</strong>, tap off any excess, then add them to the <strong>milk </strong>and finally press them into the <strong>breadcrumbs </strong>firmly to coat evenly</p><p>Add the <strong>breaded chicken strips </strong>to a separate baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 15-18 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) and golden – these are your <strong>homemade chicken goujons</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-1696425930679-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-1696425930679-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-1696425930679-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-1696425930679-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
