          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-1696425930679-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the chicken goujons are cooking, boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop your<strong> brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Heat a pot with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1648027632360-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
