          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1648027643725-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>homemade</strong> <strong>chicken goujons</strong> with the<strong> beans </strong>and <strong>potato</strong> <strong>wedges</strong> to the side</p><p>Top the beans with the<strong> remaining grated cheese </strong>and garnish with the<strong> sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Loved this recipe? Us too! That’s why it’s one of our Everyday Favourites, available every week.</span></strong></p>",
